96b62e18-f71c-419e-b915-f325f42f981c.title: Kamfreena
96b62e18-f71c-419e-b915-f325f42f981c.text:
Why hello there! I'm Kamfreena. Like the look of my
pets? I think they're eyeing you up.

67ba2a52-03e7-43f1-86a5-9b98ce4ecc77.title: <player>
67ba2a52-03e7-43f1-86a5-9b98ce4ecc77.text: That was a really bad pun.

dfe52a78-34c7-4e45-9fb4-0ce2153de398.title: Kamfreena
dfe52a78-34c7-4e45-9fb4-0ce2153de398.text:
Sorry... I don't get to see the rest of the guild much,
stuck up here. The Cyclopes don't talk much you see.

21834b51-53f3-4368-bd1b-df46e39e219a.title: Kamfreena
21834b51-53f3-4368-bd1b-df46e39e219a.text:
Nope! Cyclopes is the plural of cyclops. One cyclops,
many cyclopes.

3200a4fb-6cfb-4388-99a4-df975a3a805a.title: Kamfreena
3200a4fb-6cfb-4388-99a4-df975a3a805a.text: They're from the far east lands.

36903c14-fe17-4069-bc1c-26e2565a6eee.title: Kamfreena
36903c14-fe17-4069-bc1c-26e2565a6eee.text:
Ahh.. our guildmaster, Harrallak, went on an expedition
there. He brought them back with him.

ccfe5587-be6c-46d6-ab75-c8afdcc58c3c.title: Kamfreena
ccfe5587-be6c-46d6-ab75-c8afdcc58c3c.text:
For the warriors to train on of course! They also drop
a rather nice blade.

7fcb30e8-58d4-41db-a45a-73e25ac027ce.title: Kamfreena
7fcb30e8-58d4-41db-a45a-73e25ac027ce.text:
It's a blade you can defend with using your shield
hand, like I have.

de574f01-5279-4b7c-82eb-25e7eb4a39eb.title: Kamfreena
de574f01-5279-4b7c-82eb-25e7eb4a39eb.text:
For every 10 tokens you collect around the guild, you
can spend one minute in with my pets. As you get
defenders you can show them to me to earn even
better ones... but remember if you lose them you'll have

4f5313d9-356c-4c77-beab-39a6b7b3b870.title: Kamfreena
4f5313d9-356c-4c77-beab-39a6b7b3b870.text:
to start at bronze again. I'd advise keeping a spare in
your bank.

b796306a-fc77-466a-814b-b02ae7ead8c6.title: Kamfreena
b796306a-fc77-466a-814b-b02ae7ead8c6.text:
Oh, by the way, you'll need to earn 100 tokens before
I'll let you in!

a493883f-8ffb-45a7-80c1-fc0be00261c5.title: <player>
a493883f-8ffb-45a7-80c1-fc0be00261c5.text: Right, I'd better go play some games then!
